










 




Canyon Laurel Investment Fund (A) L.P. $750,000,000 Financing | Newest SEC Filings

















Newest Filings











Canyon Laurel Investment Fund (A) L.P. $750,000,000 Financing
Canyon Laurel Investment Fund (A) L.P. just submitted form D announcing $750,000,000 financing.  This is a new filing. Canyon Laurel Investment Fund (A) L.P. was able to sell $69,520,000. That is 9% of the round of financing. The total private offering amount was $750,000,000. The financing was made by 14 investors. Minimal accepted investment was $0. The financing document was filed on 2016-12-27. Canyon Laurel Investment Fund (A) L.P. is based in  2000 AVENUE OF THE STARS, 11TH FLOOR  LOS ANGELES 90067. The firm's business is Pooled Investment Fund. The firm's revenue range is Decline to Disclose. The form was signed by  n/a Canyon Laurel Fund GP Co. LLC.





SEC FORM D


The Securities and Exchange Commission has not necessarily reviewed the information in this filing and has not determined if it is accurate and complete.The reader should not assume that the information is accurate and complete.



