Newest Filings











Canyon Laurel Investment Fund Cayman (B) L.P. $750,000,000 Financing
Canyon Laurel Investment Fund Cayman (B) L.P. just submitted form D announcing $750,000,000 financing.  This is a new filing. Canyon Laurel Investment Fund Cayman (B) L.P. was able to sell $70,250,000. That is 9% of the round of financing. The total private offering amount was $750,000,000. The financing was made by 17 investors. Minimal accepted investment was $0. The financing document was filed on 2017-06-14. Canyon Laurel Investment Fund Cayman (B) L.P. is based in  MAPLES CORPORATE SERVICES LIMITED UGLAND HOUSE, SOUTH CHURCH STREET GRAND CAYMAN KY1-1104. The firm's business is Pooled Investment Fund. The firm's revenue range is Decline to Disclose. The form was signed by  n/a CPRE General Partner Company LLC.





SEC FORM D


The Securities and Exchange Commission has not necessarily reviewed the information in this filing and has not determined if it is accurate and complete.The reader should not assume that the information is accurate and complete.



